purſued by the clamours and curſes of the people
for oppreſſing them. Here we muſt diſtinguiſh, that
we may the more ſafely teach: The peoples curſe
is two-fold,The peoples curſe two-fold. either cauſed, or cauſeleſſe; iuſt, or
vniuſt; either iuſtly procured by ſome reall wrong
